  "title": "Croatian Chickpea Flour Wrap",
  "description": "Intensely umami, snappy, cozy Croatian dish featuring chickpea flour, steamed in a leaf wrap. Rajasic and Ayurvedic friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
