  "instructions": [
    "Mix chickpea flour and water in a bowl to form a smooth batter.",
    "Add mung bean sprouts, kalamata olives, garlic, parsley, sun-dried tomatoes, red pepper flakes, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper to the bowl. Mix well.",
    "Heat a non-stick pan over medium heat. Pour 1 tablespoon of oil and swirl to coat.",
    "Using a ladle, pour 1/2 cup of the batter into the pan and spread evenly to form a small circle.",
    "Cook for 2 minutes or until the edges start to curl and the surface is dry.",
    "Flip the wrap and cook for another minute.",
    "Place a collard greens leaf on a plate, add the cooked wrap to the center of the leaf, and fold the leaf to enclose the wrap.",
    "Repeat with the remaining batter to make 3-4 wraps.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
